      <guid>http://www.chendongdong.net/2017/12/02/Hexo%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E6%80%BB%E7%BB%93/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 01 Dec 2017 23:58:23 GMT</pubDate>
      <description>
      
        
        
          &lt;h1 id=&quot;Hexo中一些常用总结&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#Hexo中一些常用总结&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;Hexo中一些常用总结&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;Hexo中一些常用总结&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;1. 添加图片&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;关于资源的加
        
      
      </description>
      
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<h1 id="Hexo中一些常用总结"><a href="#Hexo中一些常用总结" class="headerlink" title="Hexo中一些常用总结"></a>Hexo中一些常用总结</h1><p><strong>1. 添加图片</strong><br>关于资源的加载最好是放置在云服务器上根据链接去访问。<br>例如用<a href="https://www.qiniu.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">七牛云</a>、阿里云等。<br><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">![“图片描述”](图片地址)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><hr><p><strong>2. 添加音视频</strong><br>生成外部链接后直接添加：<br><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;iframe   </span><br><span class="line">    height=<span class="number">498</span> width=<span class="number">510</span>   </span><br><span class="line">    src=<span class="string">"http://player.youku.com/embed/XNjcyMDU4Njg0"</span>   </span><br><span class="line">    frameborder=<span class="number">0</span> allowfullscreen&gt;  </span><br><span class="line">&lt;<span class="regexp">/iframe&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><hr><p><strong>3. 关于博文中添加空格</strong><br><figure class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">半方大的空白&amp;ensp;或&amp;#8194;</span><br><span class="line">全方大的空白&amp;emsp;或&amp;#8195;</span><br><span class="line">不断行的空白格&amp;nbsp;或&amp;#160;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><p><strong>4. 关于博文中字体和颜色字号</strong><br><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;font face=<span class="string">"黑体"</span>&gt;我是黑体字&lt;<span class="regexp">/font&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="regexp">&lt;font face="微软雅黑"&gt;我是微软雅黑&lt;/</span>font&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;font face=<span class="string">"STCAIYUN"</span>&gt;我是华文彩云&lt;<span class="regexp">/font&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="regexp">&lt;font color=#0099ff size=12 face="黑体"&gt;黑体&lt;/</span>font&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;font color=#00ffff size=3&gt;null&lt;/font&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&lt;font color=gray size=<span class="number">5</span>&gt;gray&lt;<span class="regexp">/font&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><hr><p><strong>5. 关于博文中背景色设置</strong><br><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&lt;table&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td bgcolor=red&gt;背景色是：red&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><hr><p><strong>6. 添加algolia搜索</strong><br>algolia搜索感觉还是一款高逼格的检索,<a href="https://www.algolia.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">algolia官网</a><br><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo algolia</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p><hr><p><strong>7. 关于博文中添加评论</strong><br>目前的评论还是liveRe展示的效果比较好些，<a href="https://livere.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">liveRe官网</a></p><hr><p><strong>*. 常用的命令</strong></p><figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo <span class="keyword">new</span> page categories</span><br><span class="line">hexo <span class="keyword">new</span> page tags</span><br><span class="line">hexo g</span><br><span class="line">hexo d</span><br><span class="line">npm install hexo-server --save</span><br><span class="line">npm install hexo-admin --save</span><br><span class="line">npm install hexo-generator-archive --save</span><br><span class="line">npm install hexo-generator-feed --save</span><br><span class="line">npm install hexo-generator-search --save</span><br><span class="line">npm install hexo-generator-tag --save</span><br><span class="line">npm install hexo-deployer-git --save</span><br><span class="line">npm install hexo-generator-sitemap --save</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">#字数统计</span><br><span class="line">npm install hexo-wordcount --save</span><br><span class="line">#检索</span><br><span class="line">npm install hexo-algolia@<span class="number">0.2</span><span class="number">.0</span> --save</span><br><span class="line">hexo algolia</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content:encoded>
      
      <comments>http://www.chendongdong.net/2017/12/02/Hexo%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E6%80%BB%E7%BB%93/#disqus_thread</comments>
    </item>
    
